argument.p:
The occasion of renewing the Discourse;
the going to Langius his Gardens.
Their commendations.

That there are divers sorts of punishments;
some occult and internal,
which accompany the crime it self;
and which the wicked never escape.
That such are more grievous than
any external ones.

div.p:
At Caesaraea by the inhabitants out


of hate to the Nation and their Religion;
twenty thousand.

At Alexandria in AEgypt under Tyberius
Alexander the then Governour;
fifty thousand.
